{"tid":1474450,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉劉淑儀支持透過法律手段以緊急條例禁止示威","createTime":"2019-08-15T07:35:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T08:12:05.000Z","uid":66324,"like":13,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"204e6a83fb043225fd9971b0478cde5b8bfec0fe","tid":1474450,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:35:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474790-20190815.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474790-20190815.htm&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdvQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=6940c15a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474790-20190815.htm&h=f2fd305a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474790-20190815.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員兼新民黨立法會議員葉劉淑儀表示，警隊面對現時的局面很艱難，相對消防和救護，警隊的工作較有爭議，她又指，有人怪責警隊處理示威太軟弱和出動太慢，也明白有市民對警方的處理有不滿，但認為警方可以調動的人不多，要靠警隊承擔保護安全的責任。<br />\n<br />\n她在本台節目《千禧年代》表示，聯合國人權專員早前對香港警方使用催淚彈的講法，只是回應示威人士的投訴，又指對方未有實地了解，很難透過片段作評論。她又認為，現時年輕人可能誤解何謂自由，自由是要有秩序和尊重他人，希望他們可以和平散去，不用政府出動更嚴厲法例處理示威。<br />\n<br />\n對於星期日當晚接受傳媒訪問時指，警方不可能喬裝示威者，葉劉淑儀解釋，當日是對喬裝的講法感到錯愕，又指，網上好多消息和流言，事後理解認為警方以「放蛇」的方式處理，也不是不合理，強調警方不會做違法的事。<br />\n<br />\n另外，警方未有跟隨港澳辦的講法，表示香港有恐怖主義的苗頭，葉劉淑儀認為，示威者掟氣油彈行為很危險，又批評襲擊警察宿舍的行為很恐佈。被問到行為恐佈是否等同恐怖主義，葉劉淑儀說，她並沒有作界定，承認現時的情況未達法例對恐怖主義的定義。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀表示，現時香港的事態非常嚴重，又支持另一名行政會議成員湯家驊提出，透過法律手段，以緊急條例禁止示威，止暴制亂，重申過往香港被評為最安全的城市，現時招牌被「打爛」，令人非常痛心。"},{"pid":"66c653bf302a40c11599b17d2eef382fe91c9183","tid":1474450,"uid":167581,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:36:02.000Z","msg":"佢真係好想妹妹死"},{"pid":"02a12001a5c56467922dc6039eb43cd27b9ed842","tid":1474450,"uid":21873,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:36:14.000Z","msg":"又起風了"},{"pid":"c8e0d4895ff05855a11551a9f4a23bece88f505c","tid":1474450,"uid":39221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:36:20.000Z","msg":"正呀<br />\n禁埋市民帶ppe啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd6de154a44ca6a658ab0a048a7adbbed474c12","tid":1474450,"uid":61228,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:36:43.000Z","msg":"黑警自己認左有臥底混入帶頭搞事"},{"pid":"140e4962861b254286f9126d51aa6056b7681646","tid":1474450,"uid":226569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:36:51.000Z","msg":"【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n// The UK should give Hong Kong citizens full UK nationality as a means of reassurance amid the current standoff with Beijing, the chair of the influential Commons foreign affairs committee has argued. (The Guardian)//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅take返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打000000 或 N/A<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdvQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=9d78a5ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"3a5dfc2c216c6460afab43de5bc8129d1f8819b4","tid":1474450,"uid":21873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:37:19.000Z","msg":"孽瘤隨風擺"},{"pid":"3272cfab0067a45da19aad1f568bf7eccd321bd9","tid":1474450,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png&h=4a3dc024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg&h=42d70b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c59971ccd4942bdc7c51b9fff04823916d060d4","tid":1474450,"uid":122275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:37:38.000Z","msg":"禁止左就冇人出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我生日請食飯有冇人出？"},{"pid":"4cb302724a04a96b09edf52842317f7d1fd000a8","tid":1474450,"uid":296712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:37:56.000Z","msg":"咁不如用緊急條例將大家送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e0c08e8008765c0dde41b65dfc9588327bb145","tid":1474450,"uid":133412,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:38:45.000Z","msg":"爭你老母議咩，擺明係濫暴啦，咪再發夢啦，你個格無得變，格無變，做唔到特首，你個妹妹都做到，你做唔到，咪係你廢囉，成日死出嚟講嘢托柒咩。"},{"pid":"4b2d6d046fda0632dfcd13d44c77bab5f9a5ba73","tid":1474450,"uid":76674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:38:49.000Z","msg":"就算你禁到示威，你禁得住市民既怒火？"},{"pid":"040a91fd9b2ebe28d753fb57170949974faf48c9","tid":1474450,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:39:16.000Z","msg":"真係好恨做香港市長喎"},{"pid":"ddd791b99483df7c882bf8d7c8dc0e0e2b7fc70d","tid":1474450,"uid":189430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:39:27.000Z","msg":"佢真係好撚痴線<br />\n要幫林鄭補幾多下刀?"},{"pid":"1d5263d92898e19140268c25eaf8b061ea6ec390","tid":1474450,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:39:46.000Z","msg":"點解唔緊急條例的陳同佳去台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b6c1ab2924e396fb0c941bc9948d5d04b3f148","tid":1474450,"uid":273854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:40:04.000Z","msg":"支持出禁制令<br />\n限制警察權力<br />\n<br />\n【法律JJ】如何用法律去限制警隊濫權<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1380667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1380667</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nground:<br />\n基本法28條<br />\n香港居民的人身自由不受侵犯。&nbsp;<br />\n香港居民不受任意或非法逮捕、拘留、監禁。禁止任意或非法搜查居民的身體、剝奪或限制居民的人身自由。禁止對居民施行酷刑、任意或非法剝奪居民的生命。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nfacts:<br />\n1. 警察非法拘捕 (例如影相告阻差辦工/襲警)<br />\n2. 警察惡意拘捕 (大部份被捕人士都係拘捕後被無條件釋放)<br />\n3. 警察犯法無監管 (拘捕示威人士後摳打佢地, 示威者已經離開緊繼續攻擊)<br />\n<br />\napply (禁制令/ 司法覆核)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 禁止明顯犯刑事, 而警察內部無對佢地作出調查嘅警員繼續職務(停職)。<br />\n2. 在處理公眾集會時，禁止沒有展示能識別身份的警員執行職務。(要有明顯睇到嘅ID no., 未必要係委任證或警員編號)<br />\n3. 警隊條例需要加入實質有效監察權力的條文。</span><br />\n<br />\n尤其係禁制令<br />\n1. 暫時將某啲警員停職, 並沒有 irreversible consequency.&nbsp;<br />\n2. 繼續比佢地行駛警權, 好大機會會對市民造成irreversible damage。(好多影片可以做證)<br />\n3. 禁制令可以緊急申請。"},{"pid":"0d2a7ba5ed0874a5a3a03e3f7446f860fe898bd6","tid":1474450,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:40:31.000Z","msg":"宣佈戒嚴囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你又淆底唔敢做"},{"pid":"2b0a1e572192d785c18ef85e59138d01126fdf0d","tid":1474450,"uid":32588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:40:57.000Z","msg":"又係宵禁<br />\n講咗好耐都未做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"837b744f945d54af7181d23eb3332a244794e603","tid":1474450,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:41:22.000Z","msg":"禁止市民戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9556980a608f25a8d514875ffdfc538b05006d68","tid":1474450,"uid":50670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:42:34.000Z","msg":"可以理解當年點解會做保安局局長做到辭職，啲諗法同說話放喺今日都係相當瘋狂"},{"pid":"3611bdb44d8604991d62802a251c1c72ff8f9956","tid":1474450,"uid":251556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:42:59.000Z","msg":"禁止矇面法 <br />\n大聲D 繼續啦 你班犯法既人"},{"pid":"41fe1cc29d1f05cacc840b79689446c8218db778","tid":1474450,"uid":288900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:43:21.000Z","msg":"其實只要回應5大訴求,咁咪唔會再有示威囉....成班行政會議都廢既"},{"pid":"92614c211e82170d99b234871ee7de2a8fa7ce26","tid":1474450,"uid":302917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:44:13.000Z","msg":"佢真係好憎林鄭唔係講笑"},{"pid":"9a349e8dc37e0b77678af9307916587f216f5674","tid":1474450,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:44:33.000Z","msg":"呢條友都一鋪清袋<br />\n本來條友係sell專業，sell中產<br />\n<br />\n但今次形象蕩然無存<br />\n<br />\n想選超區已經無左件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d9680186de70df60a222739e9857045b2bd7c5","tid":1474450,"uid":189430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a349e8dc37e0b77678af9307916587f216f5674","tid":1474450,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:44:33.000Z","msg":"呢條友都一鋪清袋<br />\n本來條友係sell專業，sell中產<br />\n<br />\n但今次形象蕩然無存<br />\n<br />\n想選超區已經無左件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:46:10.000Z","msg":"佢廿三條過唔到就已經痴左線......"}]}